    <gi>
      <title>slicing (<c>[:]</c>)</title>
      <p>A <em>slice</em> is a substring of a string. Example: <c>'bananas and
cream'[3:6]</c> evaluates to <c>ana</c> (so does <c>'bananas and
cream'[1:4]</c>).</p>
    </gi>
